  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b9e\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u00a0\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc6\u0ba9 \u0b8e\u0bae\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bae\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Don't name us guilty of Easter Sunday bombings - Maithri pleads",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the April 21 bomb attack report, if I am found guilty, the prosecution would have filed a case against me. But only human rights and compensation have been filed.",
        "Therefore, former President Maithripala Sirisena said in the House that he completely rejects mentioning us as the culprit of the April 21 bombings.",
        "He made a special statement when the Parliament met yesterday under the chairmanship of the Speaker and mentioned the above in his speech.",
        "People's Liberation Front leader Anurakumara Dissanayake, United People's Shakti leader, opposition leader Sajith Premadasa and the Sri Lanka Freedom Party are said to have not come forward to take over the government.",
        "The Sri Lanka Freedom Party initiated negotiations with the President six months ago regarding the establishment of an all-party government.",
        "We have mentioned to the President, the country and the Parliament that if an all-party government is established, one of them is ready.",
        "Over the past two years, the ruling and opposition sides have raised various issues about the contents of the report submitted by the Presidential Commission of Inquiry into the April 21 bomb attack.",
        "If the case could have been filed based on the report submitted by the Presidential Commission of Inquiry, the law department would have filed the case.",
        "In connection with the April 21 bomb attack, 8 cases have been filed in the High Commission for Human Rights, and around 400 cases have been filed in the Negombo and Colombo High Courts seeking compensation from the Prime Minister and the Chief of Police.",
        "I appointed the Presidential Commission of Inquiry into the April 21 bombings. The recommendations stated that I could have had advance knowledge of the April 21 bombings.",
        "According to the report of the Presidential Commission of Inquiry, the case could have been filed if it could have been filed. But now only human rights and compensation have been filed.",
        "I therefore reject the matters mentioned in the Commission's report based on the views of the legal counsel.",
        "I clearly state that I am not the culprit of April 21 bombing."
      ],
